2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - Topic modeling is a popular technique in natural language processing, which falls under this category. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new model that integrates clustering and topic modeling, which is a machine learning task. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed model uses variational inference, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.DB (Databases) - Document clustering is often used in database systems for organizing and retrieving documents.
